com.poesys.db.col
Class CompareColumnVisitor

java.lang.Object
  com.poesys.db.col.CompareColumnVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IColumnVisitor
public class CompareColumnVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IColumnVisitor

Implements the IColumnVisitor Visitor pattern interface to do a compareTo operation on two objects of the same type.

Author:
Robert J. Muller
